column13: The Bangkok Game Festival is a two-day event that celebrates the world of video games. The festival will feature a variety of activities{&(thinkk-better-comma#1789)&} including:{&(thinkk-better-newline#3389)&}{&(thinkk-better-newline#3389)&}- Game demos: Attendees will be able to try out the latest and greatest video games from all over the world.{&(thinkk-better-newline#3389)&}- Cosplay contest: Attendees will be able to participate in a cosplay contest to show off their best video game-inspired costumes.{&(thinkk-better-newline#3389)&}- Esports tournaments: There will be a variety of esports tournaments held throughout the festival{&(thinkk-better-comma#1789)&} including tournaments for Dota 2{&(thinkk-better-comma#1789)&} League of Legends{&(thinkk-better-comma#1789)&} and CS:GO.{&(thinkk-better-newline#3389)&}- Developer panels: Attendees will have the opportunity to learn from and interact with video game developers from all over the world.
